Cell["\<\
This suggests that the image could be significantly compressed without \
loosing any information.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.938762183352606*^9, 
  3.938762203769476*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"144ae053-bce4-e749-8960-\
5aa52f12e7dc"],

Cell["\<\
In principle, one could use KMC to identify 76 695 colour clusters in the \
image. However, this would be slow. It would be more efficient to do a loop \
over all the unique colours and identify the pixels coordinates of the pixels \
that correspond to each colour.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.938762212105488*^9, 
  3.938762323106785*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"96e0224d-f20b-da49-9e3d-\
1d16643d4605"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
},
